71.1	Going_postal	Going postal	Going postal, in American English slang, means becoming extremely and uncontrollably angry, often to the point of violence, and usually in a workplace environment.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/58/1986-post-office-killing-spree-statue.jpg/220px-1986-post-office-killing-spree-statue.jpg
